sentences: Mark Potsic, better known by his stage name DJ Nu-Mark (born June 10, 1971), is an American hip hop producer and DJ.
In 2004, the Hands On mixtape was released on Sequence Records.
In 2012, DJ Nu-Mark released the album titled Broken Sunlight on Hot Plate Records.
In 2014, Slimkid3 & DJ Nu-Mark, his collaborative album with Slimkid3, was released on Delicious Vinyl.
